Scenario: Finding customer's email address. (Success Case)

“Given that I am a seller of the website,
And I want to find a customer's email address,
When I open the "Orders" page,
And I click on the "Order details" of a specific order,
And I look at the customer's information,
Then I should be able to find the customer's email to contact them."




Scenario: Finding customer's email address. (Failure Case)

“Given that I am a seller of the website,
And I want to find a customer's email address,
When I open the "Orders" page,
And I search for a specific order using the order confirmation number,
And I enter the wrong confirmation number,
Then the page would display that there was no order with that confirmation number found."
